name: Skydiver Cat
description:
• Skydiver Cat is a game where you take the role of a cat with one specific goal, catch the highest amount of fish you can collect.
  • Play with different types of cats, we have from some cute little cats, a chef or even a robot!!!!
  • Beware of anvils and pigeons that will be over there, or your cat will not be happy.

This game was a project made for a university exam. If this game receives support, there is a possibility that in the future we will improve it.

Enjoy!!!
